Upload your CV




| Field            | Description                                     |
| ---------------- | ----------------------------------------------- |
| `id`             | Primary key                                     |
| `user_id`        | Foreign key to auth table                       |
| `display_name`   | Full name or business name                      |
| `headline`       | Tagline or title                                |
| `bio`            | About the user or business                      |
| `linkedin_url`   | Public LinkedIn profile                         |
| `profile_image`  | URL of profile image                            |
| `website_url`    | Business or personal site                       |
| `tags`           | JSON array of expertise or industries           |
| `content_themes` | Focus areas (e.g., SEO, social media, branding) |
| `location`       | Optional city or country                        |
| `import_source`  | Enum (e.g., 'manual', 'linkedin', 'resume')     |
